rows.label: qst200217_msg0001
rows.name:
Seems like Harghal intends
to use Luxuria as a base
to smuggle Pollen Orbs to each nation.

rows.label: qst200217_msg0003
rows.name:
Because Luxuria has only recently
ended its isolation.

rows.label: qst200217_msg0004
rows.name:
Since import routes haven't been
established, even if you bring suspicious
things, it might be hard to trace.

rows.label: qst200217_msg0005
rows.name:
Trying to do bad things in my country,
they're 100 years too early!

rows.label: qst200217_msg0006
rows.name:
Harghal will probably
come to receive the cargo at Genbu
Port. We'll catch her at the scene!

rows.label: qst200217_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Uooooooh! I'll round up all
the petty villains who dye their hands
in smuggling in one fell swoop!
